{"article_id":"uxE0GeAN091KgAR3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Sen. Susan Collins ' announcement Friday","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that she would vote `` yes '' on Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"likely ended the uncertainty over his confirmation .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"But","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"while Collins spoke on the Senate floor","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"and explained","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"why she would be voting for Kavanaugh ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"people angry over her decision","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"were donating cash","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"to defeat her in her next election .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"More than $ 50,000 was given over the course of her nearly 45-minute speech ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"bringing the total","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"raised on an online crowdfunding campaign","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"to defeat Collins in her 2020 election","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"to more than $ 3 million as of 7 p.m .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"The campaign by three activists groups , Be A Hero Team , Maine People 's Alliance and Mainers for Accountable Leadership , had been criticized by Collins and others over several weeks as a possible attempt","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"to bribe Collins into voting against Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"The groups started raising money in August ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"asking people across the nation to donate to Collins ' opponent in an attempt","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to show her the stark opposition to Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"No one has yet filed","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"to run against Collins in 2020 .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Susan Rice , former President Barack Obama 's National Security Adviser and United Nations Ambassador , suggested on Twitter Friday","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that she could challenge Collins .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"The donation page ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"titled `` Either Sen. Collins VOTES NO on Kavanaugh","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"OR we fund her future opponent ''","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"went down briefly on crowdfunding website crowdpac.com Friday afternoon","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"because of `` overwhelming '' traffic to the page ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Be a Hero said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"The groups are also raising money on the website ActBlue","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"and say","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"in total , between the two the amount has topped $ 3 million .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"The groups say","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"donations are coming in every three seconds .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"Sen. Susan Collins a 'yes ' on Kavanaugh ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"drawing anger from protesters and praise from GOP","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh moves towards Supreme Court confirmation","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"after Susan Collins , Joe Manchin pledge support","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"The page has said","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"those donating would n't be charged","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"if Collins voted no on Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"But on Friday , Collins seemingly put an end to the uncertainty ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"giving a nearly 45-minute speech on the Senate floor","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that explained her process and why she 'd be voting","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"to confirm him .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"`` Susan Collins has betrayed the people , and especially the women and survivors , of Maine , ''","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"the campaign organizers said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"`` Thousands of Mainers wrote ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"called ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"visited ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"protested ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"begged","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"and pleaded with Susan Collins to do the right thing","depth":16},{"id":57,"text":"- to be a hero -","depth":16},{"id":58,"text":"and vote no .","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"She ignored them . ''","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"The statement continued ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"`` For years she has claimed to be an independent , a different kind of Republican ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"but today she shattered that facade forever .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Her vote will reverberate","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"long after she has left the Senate . ''","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"The organizers said","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"they were committed to defeating Collins in 2020","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and pledged to `` never let her forget '' this decision .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"`` Maine deserves a Senator","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"who would recoil at the idea","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"of confirming a proven liar , an emotionally unstable partisan , to the Supreme Court , ''","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"the statement said .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"`` Maine deserves a Senator","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"who will believe survivors ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"who will listen to their stories ,","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"and who will represent them with honor .","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Susan Collins is no longer capable of that . ''","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"During her speech on the floor , Collins went through the issues , from Obamacare , same-sex marriage and abortion rights ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Kavanaugh 's record and pledges before Congress were enough","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"to keep her vote .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"She said","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford ,","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"who alleged","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"Kavanaugh sexually assaulted her","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"when they were teens ,","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"offered a compelling testimony before Congress ,","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"but ultimately no one could vouch for her claims","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"or even remember the party .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Collins said","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"the allegations , in her eyes , `` fail to meet the 'more likely than not ' '' standard .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"She said","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"she believes","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"voting against Kavanaugh","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"without witnesses or proof","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"could start a `` dangerous '' precedent .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"`` I do not believe","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"that these charges can fairly prevent Judge Kavanaugh from serving on the court , ''","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Collins said ,","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"that her decision should not be `` misconstrued as suggesting","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"that unwanted sexual contact of any nature is not a serious problem in this country . ''","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"A watchdog group asked the Justice Department to investigate the campaign against Collins out of concern","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"the money donated was an attempt","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"to bribe Collins ' vote","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"and called it illegal .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"It 's illegal","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"if `` the payments are made in return for an explicit promise or undertaking by the official","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"to perform or not to perform an official act , ''","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"the Foundation for Accountability and Civic Trust","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"( FACT )","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"wrote in a letter to the Justice Department .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":0,"right":222,"relation":"organization","nucl